AsaanSafar Android Application Package (.APK) Placeholder.
To replace this file with your actual fully functional mobile app:
1. Compile your Android App in Android Studio as detailed in MOBILE_APP_GUIDE.md.
2. Copy your compiled 'app-release.apk' into the 'public/' directory of this project and rename it to 'AsaanSafar.apk'.
3. Your users will then be able to download the real working app instantly from this button!
